        <p>Rating component</p>
        <h3>Basic Usage</h3>
        <p>
            The rating is divided into three levels by default. You can use the
            <code>colors</code>
            array to grade the score and its sentiment (colors are not distinguished by default). The colors corresponding to the three levels are set using the
            <code>colors</code>
            attribute, while their thresholds are defined by
            <code>low-threshold</code>
            and
            <code>high-threshold</code>
            . You can also customize segments by passing a color object, where the keys are the segment boundaries and the values are their corresponding colors.
        </p>
